@startuml seq_08_browse_post
title Sequence Diagram: UC-08 Browse Post

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Post Controller" as Controller
participant "Post Service" as Service
participant "Redis Cache" as Redis
participant "Post Repository" as Repo

User -> Frontend: Open Forum Homepage
Frontend -> Controller: GET /api/posts/public-feed
Controller -> Service: Get Public Feed
Service -> Redis: Check Cache for Feed
alt Cache Hit
    Redis --> Service: Cached Feed Data
else Cache Miss
    Redis --> Service: Null
    Service -> Repo: Fetch Recent Public Posts
    Repo --> Service: List of Posts
    Service -> Redis: Store Feed in Cache (TTL)
end
Service --> Controller: Feed Data
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: Display Post List

User -> Frontend: Click on a specific post
Frontend -> Controller: GET /api/posts/{post_id}
Controller -> Service: Get Post Details
Service -> Repo: Fetch Post by ID
Repo --> Service: Post Details
Service --> Controller: Post Details
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: Display full post content
@enduml